[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I have completed initial reconnaissance on the target system (http://127.0.0.1:33050). Here's the complete analysis:                                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Discovered Endpoints                                                                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
