[32m│[0m ### Key Security Findings                                                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **1. SQL Injection in category parameter (CONFIRMED)**                                                                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Type:** Error-based and Boolean-based blind SQL injection                                                                                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Location:** GET parameter `category` on homepage (`/?category=`)                                                                                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Evidence:**                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Single quote injection triggers MySQL error: `"Error in query: You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m use near '\'' at line 1"`                                                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Filter bypass works using `/**/` instead of spaces                                                                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Column count: 1 column (confirmed via ORDER BY testing)                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **2. Space-Filter Bypass**                                                                                                                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Filters block `SELECT`, `UNION` when used with spaces                                                                                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Successfully bypassed using `/**/` comment syntax as space replacement                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Working payload pattern: `Nature'/**/AND/**/'x'=(select/**/...)-- -`                                                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **3. Error Information Disclosure**                                                                                                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - PHP errors reveal file paths: `/var/www/html/index.php`                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - MySQL error messages expose database type and version                                                                                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Query structure partially visible through error messages                                                                                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Database Information Extracted                                                                                                                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Database name:** "blog_db" (confirmed via boolean-based extraction)                                                                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Column count:** 1 column in the posts query                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
